  <entry>
    <title>工具学习</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/01/12/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/01/12/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</id>
    <published>2021-01-12T14:30:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-13T05:05:41.322Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录一些会用到的工具<a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="Git-amp-Github"><a href="#Git-amp-Github" class="headerlink" title="Git&amp;Github"></a>Git&amp;Github</h2><h3 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h3><ol><li>安装<br>win：到官网下<br>linux：<code>sudo apt-get install git</code></li></ol><p><code>mkdir repository_name</code></p><p><a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/896043488029600">廖雪峰的官方网站</a></p><hr><h2 id="Markdown"><a href="#Markdown" class="headerlink" title="Markdown"></a>Markdown</h2><ol><li><p>标题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D; 一级标题  </span><br><span class="line">--- 二级标题 </span><br><span class="line"># 一级标题 </span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题 </span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>段落<br>两个以上空格加回车or两端之家使用一个空行</p></li><li><p>字体</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体* _斜体_</span><br><span class="line">**粗体** __粗体__</span><br><span class="line">***粗斜体*** ___粗斜体___ </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>分割线</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">* * *</span><br><span class="line">******</span><br><span class="line">- - -</span><br><span class="line">------</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除线</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~文本~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>下划线</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;u&gt;文本&lt;&#x2F;u&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>脚注</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[^需要注明的文本]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">创建脚注格式 [^Markdown]</span><br><span class="line">[^Markdown]: 这是markdown的脚注</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">8. 列表</span><br><span class="line">无序列表：*&#x2F;+&#x2F;-</span><br><span class="line">有序列表：1. </span><br><span class="line">嵌套列表：在子列表前加四个空格&#x2F;TAB</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>区块引用</p></li></ol><ul><li>普通引用<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;xxx</span><br><span class="line">&gt;xxx</span><br><span class="line">&gt;xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>嵌套引用<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;最外层</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;第一层</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;第二层嵌套</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>区块中使用列表<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; 区块中使用列表</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 1. 第一项</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 2. 第二项</span><br><span class="line">&gt; - 第一项</span><br><span class="line">&gt; - 第二项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>列表中使用区块<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 第一项</span><br><span class="line">&gt;区块1</span><br><span class="line">&gt;区块2</span><br><span class="line">- 第二项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ol start="10"><li>代码</li></ol><ul><li>单行函数<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#96;printf()&#96; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>区块代码<br>四个空格或TAB<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   printf()</span><br><span class="line">printf()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>用两行<code>包裹一段代码，可以在第一行</code>后面选择编程语言</li></ul><ol start="11"><li> 链接</li></ol><ul><li>普通链接<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[name](URL)</span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line">&lt;URL&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>高级链接：通过一个变量来设置链接，变量赋值在文档末尾（好处是多次被使用时候方便修改）<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">用xxx作为网址变量 [name][xxx]</span><br><span class="line">[xxx]: URL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ol start="12"><li>图片<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![alt 属性文本](图片地址)</span><br><span class="line">![alt 属性文本](图片地址 &quot;可选标题&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">![皮卡丘](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ss2.bdstatic.com&#x2F;70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy&#x2F;it&#x2F;u&#x3D;1558026985,2729915815&amp;fm&#x3D;26&amp;gp&#x3D;0.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>高级链接的操作也可以用在图片上<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">用xxx作为网址变量 [皮卡丘][xxx]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[xxx]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ss2.bdstatic.com&#x2F;70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy&#x2F;it&#x2F;u&#x3D;1558026985,2729915815&amp;fm&#x3D;26&amp;gp&#x3D;0.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>Markdown 还没有办法指定图片的高度与宽度，如果你需要的话，你可以使用普通的 <img> 标签。<img src="http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png" width="50%"></li></ol><p>13 表格</p><pre><code>[菜鸟教程    Markdown 教程](https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-tutorial.html)---## Vim---</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;记录一些会用到的工具</summary>
    
    
    
    
