  <entry>
    <title>博客搭建笔记</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/01/12/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/01/12/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</id>
    <published>2021-01-12T04:15:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-13T04:50:56.882Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>19年底弄过一次，几个月前折腾电脑翻车了重新装了个系统，Github上面的仓库也在但我还是把以前的那个删了新建了一个，希望这个可以用久一点，记录学习过程中遇到的问题以及解决办法。</p><a id="more"></a><p>The following is a record of the process of building the blog</p><p>First install <em>node</em>，Go to the official website and download the <em>LTS</em> version.<br>cmd <code>node-v</code> <code>npm -v</code> </p><p>Domestic with Taobao mirror source for the next operation will be faster (with a ladder can be used without)<br><code>npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code><br>-g global install<br><code>cnmp -v</code></p><p>Then use <em>cnpm</em> install <em>hexo frame</em><br><code>cnpm install -g hexo-cli</code><br><code>hexo -v</code></p><p>Go to the blog directory <code>G: &amp; cd/Project/Blog</code><br>Cerate hexo frame<code>hexo init</code><br>A blog post will be generated automatically<br><code>hexo s</code> (s-server)<br>Then enter the URL <code>http://localhost:4000/</code> view</p><p>create new blog<code>hexo new &quot;blog name&quot;</code><br>Use vim,notepad or Typora writing content<br>After save exit <code>hexo clean</code><br>Generate web pages<code>hexo g</code>(g-generate)</p><p>Restart <code>heox s</code><br>You can see the previous blog on the localhost</p><p><code>cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</code></p><p>The following warnings may apply</p><p>Verion 9 of Highlight.js has reached EOL.<br>It will no longer be supported or receive security updates in the future.<br>Please upgrade to version 10 or encourage your indirect dependencies to do so.</p><p>Need to install the latest version<br><code>cnpm install highlight.js@latest</code><br>reference: <a href="https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js/issues/2882">https://github.com/highlightjs/highlight.js/issues/2882</a></p><p>Create a repository in GitHub which named <em>ooblivion(name).github.io</em><br><a href="https://github.com/ooblivion/ooblivion.github.io.git">https://github.com/ooblivion/ooblivion.github.io.git</a></p><p><code>notepad _config.yml</code><br>End of document</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: &#39;git&#39;</span><br><span class="line">repo: git@github.com:ooblivion&#x2F;ooblivion.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>git bash</em><br><code>hexo d</code></p><p>Change theme<br><code>git clone https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid.git themes/fluid</code></p><p><code>git clone https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-icarus.git themes/icarus</code></p><p><code>notepad _config.yml</code><br><code>hexo clean</code><br><code>hexo g</code><br><code>hexo s</code><br><code>hexo d</code></p><p>Conlusion<br>we need git node.js<br>Theme<br><a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/">https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/</a><br><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a><br>Reference<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty/?spm_id_from=333.788.recommend_more_video.0">手把手教你从0开始搭建自己的个人博客 |无坑版视频教程| hexo</a><br>Thanks to <a href="https://www.codesheep.cn/">Codesheep</a></p><hr><h2 id="hexo常用命令"><a href="#hexo常用命令" class="headerlink" title="hexo常用命令"></a>hexo常用命令</h2><p>hexo n “博客名称”  =&gt; hexo new “博客名称”   #这两个都是创建新文章，前者是简写模式<br>$ hexo p  =&gt; hexo publish<br>$ hexo g  =&gt; hexo generate  #生成<br>$ hexo s  =&gt; hexo server  #启动服务预览<br>$ hexo d  =&gt; hexo deploy  #部署</p><p>$ hexo server   #Hexo 会监视文件变动并自动更新，无须重启服务器。<br>$ hexo server -s   #静态模式<br>$ hexo server -p 5000   #更改端口<br>$ hexo server -i 192.168.1.1   #自定义IP<br>$ hexo clean   #清除缓存，网页正常情况下可以忽略此条命令</p><p>命令    功能<br>npm install -g hexo-cli    安装hexo-cli（hexo的命令行工具）<br>npm update -g hexo-cli    升级hexo-cli<br>hexo init 新目录名    初始化一个Hexo项目（个人静态网站）<br>hexo n [layout] “文章标题”    在Hexo项目内新建一篇文章。n == new<br>hexo g    将Hexo项目编译生成发布文档（public目录）。g == generate<br>hexo s    启动本地web服务器，可以在浏览器预览发布文档。s == server<br>hexo d    部署，将发布文档推送到个人网站。d == deploy<br>hexo cl    清除缓存文件（db.json和发布文档public目录）。cl == clean<br>hexo d -g    组合命令：生成 + 部署<br>hexo s -g    组合命令：生成 + 预览</p><hr><h2 id="参考网站"><a href="#参考网站" class="headerlink" title="参考网站"></a>参考网站</h2><p><a href="https://juejin.cn/post/6844903713811890189">https://juejin.cn/post/6844903713811890189</a><br><a href="https://kuang.netlify.app/blog/hexo.html">https://kuang.netlify.app/blog/hexo.html</a></p><p>夜间模式<br><a href="https://blog.asahih.com/hexo-icarus-night-mode/">https://blog.asahih.com/hexo-icarus-night-mode/</a><br>hexo s 报错<br><a href="https://www.haoyizebo.com/posts/710984d0/">https://www.haoyizebo.com/posts/710984d0/</a><br>博客主题自定义（很详细）<br><a href="https://www.alphalxy.com/2019/03/customize-icarus/#%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F">https://www.alphalxy.com/2019/03/customize-icarus/#%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F</a><br>这个个博客很好看<br><a href="https://blog.andycen.com/2020/03/07/Hexo-Icarus%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE/#more">https://blog.andycen.com/2020/03/07/Hexo-Icarus%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE/#more</a><br>插入图片<br><a href="http://www.monkeygeek.cn/2019/8/10/mdimage/">http://www.monkeygeek.cn/2019/8/10/mdimage/</a><br><a href="https://www.mdeditor.tw/pl/ptBs">https://www.mdeditor.tw/pl/ptBs</a><br>图床设置-PicGo<br><a href="https://picgo.github.io/PicGo-Doc/zh/guide/config.html#github%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A">https://picgo.github.io/PicGo-Doc/zh/guide/config.html#github%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A</a></p><hr><h2 id="新文章模板"><a href="#新文章模板" class="headerlink" title="新文章模板"></a>新文章模板</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">description:</span><br><span class="line">date: &#123;&#123; date &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">点击阅读前文前, 首页能看到的文章的简短描述</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- markdownlint-disable MD041 MD002--&gt; # 防止 markdownlint 报错</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="hexo-分类和标签"><a href="#hexo-分类和标签" class="headerlink" title="hexo 分类和标签"></a>hexo 分类和标签</h2><p>分类(categories)具有顺序性和层次性。Hexo 不支持指定多个同级分类。</p><p>标签(tags)没有顺序和层次。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- Diary</span><br><span class="line">- Life</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- PS3</span><br><span class="line">- Games</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上会使分类 Life 成为 Diary 的子分类, 而不是并列分类。</p><hr><p>博客的其他配置</p><ol><li>Search<br>Install search plugin<br> npm install hexo-generator-searchdb –save</li></ol><p>blog_config.yml add to the end</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  limit: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>next_config.yml false-&gt;true</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>新建页面<br>$ hexo new page “tags”<br>$ hexo new page “categories”<br>$ hexo new page “about”<br>分类有顺序，标签没顺序</li></ol><p>all done</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;19年底弄过一次，几个月前折腾电脑翻车了重新装了个系统，Github上面的仓库也在但我还是把以前的那个删了新建了一个，希望这个可以用久一点，记录学习过程中遇到的问题以及解决办法。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
